v th, icon font trn web c p dng t lc , v ngy nay n c p dng tr nn ph bin hn.</p>\n<blockquote class="pull-right"><p>\nNu bn hi, ngi no dng icons font cho web u tin? Ti khng bit. D n u tin ti dng icons font cch y cng gn hai nm ri. V lc , cc icon free cn rt t, nn ti buc phi t mnh lm ring mt b fonts icon cho d n da trn cc icon vector min ph v t to.\n</p></blockquote>\n<h5>Cch to font icon</h5>\n<p>Vic to ra font icon rt phc tp. Trc tin, bn cn phi v cc icon ra trn cc phn mm nh illustrator, corel hoc cc phn mn tng t. Sau , phi s dng phn mm to font  a cc hnh icon vector vo cc bng k t trn phn mm to font. (Hin ti, phn mm c s dng nhiu nht l <a href="http://www.high-logic.com/font-editor/fontcreator.html" target="_blank">FontCreator ca high-logic</a> gi $79)<br />\nV d: Chng ta dng font Tahoma, khi g a b c th n s ra cc k t hnh nh tng ng a b c. Nhng khi dng icon font, bn g abc th n s hin th cc icon tng ng vi k t abc.</p>\n<div class="tutorial-image"><img src="http://www.izwebz.com/wp-content/uploads/mrv2m/icons/iconic.png" alt="Icons" /></div>\n<div class="tutorial-image"><img src="http://www.izwebz.com/wp-content/uploads/mrv2m/icons/arial.png" alt="Arial" /></div>\n<p>Tuy nhin, ti ngh khng phi Web developer no cng l mt Graphic designer  c th lm 1 b icon font tng ng. Do , tt nht, bn nn dng cc b icon font min ph  p dng cho website ca mnh. Trong bi tip theo ti s lit k ra tt c cc icon font c dng ph bit, c ph v min ph.</p>\n<div class="tutorial-image"><img src="http://www.izwebz.com/wp-content/uploads/mrv2m/icons/icon.png" alt="Iconic" /></div>\n<p>Trong bi ny, ti s dng b icons font &#8220;<a href="http://somerandomdude.com/work/iconic/" target="_blank">Iconic</a>&#8221; ca P.J. Onori  lm demo. B icons font ny c 171 icon.</p>\n<h5>Cch s dng font-face</h5>\n<p>Trc tin chng ta cn phi tm hiu v cc dng @font-face . Trong video u tin ca ti v font-face th cu trc ca font-face lc  cng rt n gin. Tuy nhin, ngy nay th n  phc tp hn nhiu ri. Nguyn nhn ch yu l do cc trnh duyt h tr cc nh dng font khc nhau.<br />\nTrc tin, chng ta phi khai bo font-face trc, thng c t ngay trn cng ca tp tin stylesheet.</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n@font-face {\r\n    font-family: ''font_family_name'';\r\n    src: url(''font_name.eot'');\r\n    src: url(''font_name.eot?#iefix'') format(''embedded-opentype''),\r\n         url(''font_name.woff'') format(''woff''),\r\n         url(''font_name.ttf'') format(''truetype''),\r\n         url(''font_name.svg#SourceSansProExtraLight'') format(''svg'');\r\n    font-weight: normal;\r\n    font-style: normal;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>Sau khi khai bo xong, nu mun p dng n vo mt on paragraph, heading hoc class hoc id no . Th chng ta ch vic p cho n thuc tnh font-family, v d:</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n// font_family_name chnh l tn font family  khai bo  trn @font-face\r\nh1{font-family:font_family_name}\r\np{font-family:font_family_name}\r\n.fontface{font-family:font_family_name}\r\n// Khai bo rt gn\r\np.font {font: 18px/27px ''font_family_name'', Arial, sans-serif;}\r\n</pre>\n<h5>Cch p dng icons font vo website</h5>\n<p>Vic p dng thng ging nhau. Icon font cng ging nh font thng thi, chng ta cng import cho n vo stylesheet thng qua font-face v cng gi chng cho cc tag, selector thng qua font family.<br />\nV d </p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">@font-face { \r\n	font-family: ''IconicFill''; \r\n	src: url(''iconic_fill.eot''); \r\n	src: url(''iconic_fill.eot?#iefix'') format(''embedded-opentype''), \r\n	url(''iconic_fill.ttf'') format(''truetype''), \r\n	url(''iconic_fill.svg#iconic'') format(''svg''); \r\n	font-weight: normal; \r\n	font-style: normal; \r\n}</pre>\n<p>V chng ta ch vic khai bo th i s b p dng icon.</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">i{\r\nfont-family:IconicFill;\r\n}</pre>\n<p>By gi chng ta ch vic gi th i  html v n s p dng icons font vo cho chng ta.</p>\n<pre class="brush: xml; title: ; notranslate">&lt;p&gt;Ti ang dng icons font ny &lt;i&gt;a&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</pre>\n<p>Icons font s thay k t a khai bo v hin th  ngoi trnh duyt l icon tng ng vi k t a.</p>\n<p>Tuy nhin, mi nh pht hnh s c mt cch hng ngi dng s dng font ca h theo cch khc nhau. V d,  y b icons font ca Iconic li khc so vi cch trn. Nguyn nhn l h  lm ht cc bc trn ri, chng ta ch vic gi cc class tng ng vi icon v dng thi.</p>\n<p>Khi download v, bn s c mt th mc y  cc file hnh nh, vector, font. Trong th mc font th c hai b font &#8220;iconic fill&#8221; v &#8220;iconic stroke&#8221;. Trc tin, bn tin hnh link stylesheet iconic_stroke.css vo website ca bn.</p>\n<pre class="brush: xml; title: ; notranslate">&lt;link rel=''stylesheet'' href=''iconic_stroke.css'' type=''text/css'' media=''screen'' /&gt;</pre>\n<p>Sau , bn c vic gi cc class tng ng ra  dng thi.</p>\n<pre class="brush: xml; title: ; notranslate">&lt;span class=&quot;iconic lightbulb&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</pre>\n<p>Khi khai bo nh vy, n s hin th ra icon bng n. Vy cc bn ang t hi l lm sao bit class no  hin th icon no? Bn hy m file iconic_stroke_demo.html ln  xem cc class tng ng vi icon bn cnh.<br />\nTrong 2 class c khai bo th iconic l c nh &#8211; n khai bo font family, cn lightbulb l khai bo k t tng ng vi icon. </p>\n<div class="tutorial-image"><img src="http://www.izwebz.com/wp-content/uploads/mrv2m/icons/debug.png" alt="Debug" /></div>\n<p>V bn khng thy k t a b c d e f g nm trong the span c. Vy k t   u? Nu cc bn xem k th k t  c dng selector :before v thuc tnh content  a vo v n c m ha Hexidecimal (ci ny ch yu  bo v bn quyn font).<br />\nV d</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">.lightbulb:before{\r\ncontent: ''\\e063'';\r\n// e063 chnh l Hexidecimal Code ca k t \r\n}</pre>\n<h5>Kt lun</h5>\n<p>Icons font rt hay ng khng cc bn. Tuy nhin, khu s dng icons font th chng ta ch c th t mu cho n thi. Khng th to cc hiu ng khc nh cc icon nh bnh thng.<br />\nNgoi ra, khi s dng icons font bn cng phi bit cn nhc, nu website ca bn s dng nhiu cc icon khc nhau, th chng ta hy dng. Nu ch s dng t hn 5 icon th tt nht nn dng hnh  gii quyt. V 1 b icons font c hn 100 icon. S rt nng v lng ph ti nguyn khi dng.<br />\nCh  quan trng nht, hy c hng dn s dng ca nh pht hnh icons font  p dng cho website ca mnh. V nh ti ni pha trn, mi nh pht hnh c cc dng ring chi b font ca h.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:56:"http://www.izwebz.com/css/fonts-for-web-icon-fonts/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"2";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:45:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:24:"Fonts for web: Web fonts";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:71:"http://www.izwebz.com/video-tutorials/css-html/fonts-for-web-web-fonts/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:80:"http://www.izwebz.com/video-tutorials/css-html/fonts-for-web-web-fonts/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Tue, 23 Jul 2013 13:53:56 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:8:"CSS/HTML";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:10:"Web Design";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"x