/p>\n<h5>Google fonts API u nh?</h5>\n<p>Trong video ti hon ton khng nhc n google fonts, nguyn nhn chnh l ton b video trong series ny ti  lm cch y khong 2 nm trc, lc  cha c google fonts hoc nu c th n cng cha ph bin n mc nht nh.<br />\nGoogle fonts hin ti l mt dch v kh ph bin, nguyn nhn chnh l n min ph v mt nguyn nhn khc na  l n c h tr ting Vit v iu c bit l n hon ton rt d s dng, chng ta ch cn thao tc chn la v dng ti.</p>\n<h5>Cch s dng Web fonts</h5>\n<p>Cch p dng Web fonts vo website ca bn rt a dng, ty thuc vo cc dch v cung cp m chng ta s c cch p dng khc nhau. V c im chnh l n s qun l fonts theo domain, tc khi ng k, bn s khai bo domain website ca mnh, n x l m thy domain ca bn khng ng th s khng cho s dng.</p>\n<p>Cng kh rc ri nh? Tuy nhin, google fonts pht trin nhanh nh vy cng l c nguyn nhn. Cch s dng c n rt n gin, ch vic click chn, sao chp v s dng thi, n hon ton min ph nn ta c th p dng n vo bt k u m ta mun.</p>\n<p>Trc tin, chng ta s vo website chnh ca google fonts <a href="http://www.google.com/fonts/" title="Google fonts" target="_blank">http://www.google.com/fonts/</a>. Hin ti th google c khong 629 font families, mt con s cng kh kim tn. Khng c sc nh cc dch v c ph khc, nhng n cng va   chng ta p dng vo mt website c nhn hoc thng mi ri.<br />\nKhi quan st th chng ta thy giao din n gm 3 phn:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Tay tri: panel dng  phn loi fonts</li>\n<li>Tay phi: khu vc hin th ch  xem trc cho cc font ch</li>\n<li>Bn di mng hnh: L khu vc cc font  c chn  lm vic</li>\n</ul>\n<div class="tutorial-image"><img src="http://www.izwebz.com/wp-content/uploads/mrv2m/fontsweb/Google%20Fonts%201.png" alt="Google fonts" /></div>\n<p>Cc bn cng phi lu  l mun dng ting Vit th hy nhn bn panel phn loi, c filter l script, cc bn chn ngn ng h tr l Vietnamese chng ta c khong 12 font families  s dng, hy chn loi font m bn mun, sau  nhp vo nt &#8220;Add to Collection&#8221;  lm vic lc  th panel bn di mng hnh s hin th cho chng ta la chn, cc bn chn tip tab &#8220;Use&#8221;  qua phn p dng web fonts vo website.</p>\n<p>Gi th cc bn c th la chn cc style ca font nh  m, in nghing,&#8230;. Lu : Cng la chn nhiu th website ca chng ta s cng load lu hn y. c bit l i lc n load c ht cc thnh phn khc ri, nhng vn cha hin th ch.  l mt nhc im ca web fonts. Hy c gng ti u bng cch la chn cc font, nhng ng h &#8220;Page Load&#8221; vn  mc mu xanh.</p>\n<div class="tutorial-image"><img src="http://www.izwebz.com/wp-content/uploads/mrv2m/fontsweb/Google%20Fonts%202.png" alt="Google fonts" /></div>\n<p>c bit quan trng,  mc &#8220;Choose the character sets you want:&#8221; bn phi chn nhm k t &#8220;Vietnamese (vietnamese)&#8221; nu khng th n s khng h tr ting Vit u nh. Mun chc n th chn thm &#8220;Latin Extended (latin-ext)&#8221; na l n.</p>\n<div class="tutorial-image"><img src="http://www.izwebz.com/wp-content/uploads/mrv2m/fontsweb/Google%20Fonts%203.png" alt="Google fonts" /></div>\n<p>By gi chng ta c 3 cch chn vo website. Tuy nhin, ti vn khuyn khch cc bn dng cch @import hoc Standard, v ng n javascript th bn no yu s kh phin phc.<br />\nNu dng @import th copy on code , a vo u tp tin css ca chng ta.<br />\nNu dng kiu truyn thng Standard th ch vic copy n vo bn trong khu vc th head l n.</p>\n<div class="tutorial-image"><img src="http://www.izwebz.com/wp-content/uploads/mrv2m/fontsweb/Google%20Fonts%204.png" alt="Google fonts" /></div>\n<p>Bc cui cng, chng ta ch vic copy on code font-family  p dng vo bt k th hoc id, class no trong css m chng ta mun thi.</p>\n<div class="tutorial-image"><img src="http://www.izwebz.com/wp-content/uploads/mrv2m/fontsweb/Google%20Fonts%205.png" alt="Google fonts apply" /></div>\n<p>Lu : on code do google a ra nh.</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\nbody {\r\nfont-family: ''Open Sans Condensed'', sans-serif;\r\nfont-size: 48px;\r\ntext-shadow: 4px 4px 4px #aaa;\r\n}\r\n.web-font{\r\nfont-family: ''Open Sans Condensed'', sans-serif;\r\nfont-size: 13px;\r\nline-height:17px;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<h5>Kt lun</h5>\n<p>Tuy rng dng web fonts th rt hay, nhng m i vi Vit Nam mnh th n cng chng c sc g my, v chng cha h tr c nhiu font ting Vit p. Vn  bn quyn cng l mt phn nhc nhi, tuy nhin, bn hon ton c th gi mail v hi xin c convert font  p dng vo @font-face hoc cufon.  l cch m ti thng hay s dng khi p dng cc font ch c bit vo website ca mnh.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:76:"http://www.izwebz.com/video-tutorials/css-html/fonts-for-web-web-fonts/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"4";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:45:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:21:"Fonts for Web: Cfon";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:67:"http://www.izwebz.com/video-tutorials/css-html/fonts-for-web-cufon/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:76:"http://www.izwebz.com/video-tutorials/css-html/fonts-for-web-cufon/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Wed, 17 Jul 2013 13:22:24 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:8:"CSS/HTML";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:10:"Web Design";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:29:"http://www.izwebz.com/?p=5414";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:629:"C tng cng 3 cch  p dng mt font &#8220;ngoi&#8221; vo website ca mnh. Cufont l mt phng php rt hay. Tip tc series &#8220;Fonts for web&#8221;, hm nay th chng ta s tm hiu r hn v phng thc hot ng cng nh cc p dng Cufon vo website ca mnh. p dng cfon vo website Bn tin hnh download on script m trnh duyt tr v cho bn sau khi  convert xong. By gi chng ta s tin hnh p dng n vo website. Nhng trc tin, chng ta cng cn phi c b gii m [&#8230;]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:14:"V Minh Mn";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:5369:"<p>C tng cng 3 cch  p dng mt font &#8220;ngoi&#8221; vo website ca mnh. Cufont l mt phng php rt hay. Tip tc series &#8220;Fonts for web&#8221;, hm nay th chng ta s tm hiu r hn v phng thc hot ng cng nh cc p dng Cufon vo website ca mnh.<br />\n<span id="more-5414"></span></p>\n<div class="tutorial-image">\n<iframe width="640" height="360" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/w_fO_mbM6Ig" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div>\n<h5>p dng cfon vo website</h5>\n<p>Bn tin hnh download on script m trnh duyt tr v cho bn sau khi  convert xong. By gi chng ta s tin hnh p dng n vo website. Nhng trc tin, chng ta cng cn phi c b gii m ca cfon na ch, bn c th download n ngay ti <a href="http://cufon.shoqolate.com/" title="cufon" target="_blank">trang ch</a>. Sau khi download c 2 tp tin javascript  v ri th chng ta tin hnh chn vo website. Hai on script cn chn phi nm trong th head nh.</p>\n<pre class="brush: xml; title: ; notranslate">&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot; src=&quot;cufon-yui.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot; src=&quot;your-font-name.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</pre>\n<p>Tuy nhin, lc ny th n vn cha hot ng c u. Chng ta phi tin hnh khai bo thm bng javascript i tng no s c ch nh  dng font &#8220;ngoi&#8221;.<br />\nV d, ti  mt on code html nh sau:</p>\n<pre class="brush: xml; title: ; notranslate">&lt;h1&gt;Fonts for Web: Cfon&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Incidunt, doloribus veritatis maxime omnis culpa quisquam provident nostrum natus! Incidunt corporis dolor rerum at ducimus recusandae mollitia illum sequi ipsum sint.&lt;/p&gt;</pre>\n<p>By gi ti mun dng font &#8220;ngoi&#8221; cho th h1 th chng ta ch cn khai bo nh sau:</p>\n<pre class="brush: jscript; title: ; notranslate">&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot;&gt;\r\nCufon.replace(''h1'');\r\n&lt;/script&gt;</pre>\n<p>Hoc bn mun dng n cho .class hoc #id, hoc cc kiu selector khc th chng ta cng khai bo tng t:</p>\n<pre class="brush: jscript; title: ; notranslate">&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot;&gt;\r\nCufon.replace(''#id'');\r\nCufon.replace(''#id h1'');\r\nCufon.replace(''#id ul li:first-child'');\r\nCufon.replace(''.class'');\r\nCufon.replace(''.class1, .class2'');\r\n&lt;/script&gt;</pre>\n<p>Bn cng cn phi lu : i vi cc trnh duyt c nh IE6,7 th cn phi dng khai bo class hoc id th mi c tc dng. Vic s dng n hon ton n gin v khng qu phc tp n mc phi bc tc  suy ngh.</p>\n<div class="tutorial-image"><img src="http://www.izwebz.com/wp-content/uploads/mrv2m/fontsweb/cufon.jpg" alt="Cufon" /></div>\n<p>Cc bn nhn vo hnh nh m ti debug trn trnh duyt Chrome. Chng ta c th d dng nhn thy rng, cufont  replace cc t trong on k t ca h1 thnh cc th cavas  hin th.</p>\n<h5>Styling cho i tng dng cfon</h5>\n<p>Vic t thm mu m hoa l h cho mt i tng dng cufon th cng khng c g kh, chng ta hon ton c th style cho i tng  bng css thng thng. Tuy nhin, trong cc trng hp c bit nh hover hoc t mu dng gradient th chng ta phi dng cc phng thc do cufon cung cp  p dng. V cch s dng n cng hon ton n gin, cc bn c th xem qua wiki ca n ti a ch website ny: <a href="https://github.com/sorccu/cufon/wiki/Styling" title="Cufon wiki" target="_blank">https://github.com/sorccu/cufon/wiki/Styling</a></p>\n<h5>Dng nhiu font c c khng?</h5>\n<p>Vn   th tt nhin l c ri. Bn c th dng font ny cho tiu , font khc cho cc on paragraph,&#8230; Vic  cng khng lm kh cfon c u. Chng ta ch cn tin hnh khai bo thm font-family trong khai bo javascript Cufon.replace thi. Cc bn c th khai bo tng t theo cc sau:</p>\n<pre class="brush: xml; title: ; notranslate">&lt;script src=&quot;cufon-yui.js&quot; type=&quot;text/javascript&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;script src=&quot;Vegur_300.font.js&quot; type=&quot;text/javascript&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;script src=&quot;Myriad_Pro_400.font.js&quot; type=&quot;text/javascript&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot;&gt;\r\nCufon.replace(''h1'', { fontFamily: ''Vegur'' });\r\nCufon.replace(''h2'', { fontFamily: ''Myriad Pro'' });\r\n&lt;/script&gt;</pre>\n<h5>Kt lun</h5>\n<p>Cufon thc s rt hay, tuy nhin bn hy tri nghim n i, ri bn s dn dn pht hin ra cc im yu ca n. Trong cc bi tip theo, ti s phn tch cho cc bn thy mt mnh, yu ca tng cch dng font &#8220;ngoi&#8221; vo web.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:72:"http://www.izwebz.com/video-tutorials/css-html/fonts-for-web-cufon/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"5";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"