s pht trin ca font ch. Trong bi vit hm nay, chng ta s i vo p dng thc t bng cch p dng phng thc css 3 font-face. Trc y, ti tng c <a href="http://www.izwebz.com/video-tutorials/css-html/font-face-cho-css2/" title="Font face" target="_blank">mt video v font-face</a>. Tuy nhin, cu trc ca font-face lc  cn kh n gin. Hin ti, cch dng ca font-face  tr nn phc tp hn ri.<br />\n<span id="more-5410"></span><br />\nTrc tin, chng ta s xem qua video ny  c th bit c lch s hnh thnh ca font-face v cc chuyn i mt font ch ting Vit.</p>\n<div class="tutorial-image">\n<iframe width="640" height="360" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/zbNpLYvtm8c" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div>\n<h5>Li font ting Vit</h5>\n<p>Ti chc chn mt iu rng, rt nhiu bn s khng th no dng c ht ton b cc k t ting Vit. Trong video ti c hng dn cc cc bn dng Font Squirrel  convert v s dng c ting Vit. Tuy nhin, hm nay khi ti test li th pht hin trong b k t m Font Squirrel convert li thiu mt mt k t &#8220;&#8221;, nu bn g t &#8220;chng&#8221; th n s ch hin th &#8220;ch ng&#8221; thi.<br />\nVy ch nh b tay sao? Thc ra c rt nhiu website cho chng ta convert font. Chng ta hon ton c th la chn cc phng php thay th khc nhau. By gi chng ta c th dng website <a href="http://www.font2web.com/" target="_blank">font2web.com</a>  convert font. Cch convert th cng n gin thi, chng ta ch cn upload v download, website ny khng yu cu cc setting rm r v rc ri.</p>\n<h5>Cu trc @font-face</h5>\n<p>Trc tin, cc bn cn phi gii nn tp tin nn c tr v sau khi  convert xong. Trong  s gm cc tp tin font .woff, .eot, .ttf,&#8230; v mt tp tin font.css bn tin hnh m n ln vo xem cc on code c bn trong.  chnh l cu trc chun ca font-face trong phin bn css 3.</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n@font-face {\r\n	font-family: ''UTM_Neo'';\r\n	src: url(''fonts/UTM Neo Sans Intel.eot'');\r\n	src: local(''UTM Neo Sans Intel''), \r\n	url(''fonts/UTM Neo Sans Intel.woff'') format(''woff''), \r\n	url(''fonts/UTM Neo Sans Intel.ttf'') format(''truetype''), \r\n	url(''fonts/UTM Neo Sans Intel.svg'') format(''svg'');\r\n	font-weight: normal;\r\n	font-style: normal;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>Trong  thuc tnh font-family c khai bo  @font-face  l tn font m chng ta khai bo  s dng sau ny. src local chnh l khai bo nu nh trn my ca khch hng c font  th n s dng lun, khi phi ti v t server. Cc khai bo url chnh l ng dn n cc tp tin font ca bn.<br />\n<strong>Lu </strong>: khai bo @font-face phi  trn cng ca tp tin css. Nu bn khai bo  di th n s khng hot ng hot hot ng khng chnh xc.<br />\nSau khi khai bo @font-face xong th chng ta c th p dng n vo bt k u m chng ta mun thng qua khai bo font-family cho i tng c tham chiu. Cc bn c th xem qua cc v d di y:</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">h1{\r\n	font-family: UTM_Neo;\r\n	font-size: 20px;\r\n	font-weight: bold;\r\n}\r\n.font{\r\n	font-family: UTM_Neo;	\r\n	font-size: 15px;\r\n	font-weight: normal;\r\n}</pre>\n<p>Kt qu hin th bn c th xem trong link demo ti  ghi  ph trn.</p>\n<h5>C nn dng @font-face?</h5>\n<p>Font-face rt tin li, n gip cho chng ta rt nhiu, nhng liu dng font-face c thc s hiu qu v font-face so vi cc phng php khc nh cfon v webfont th ci no s l nht. Ti s tin hnh phn tch trong cc bi vit tip theo trong series &#8220;Fonts for web&#8221;. Cc bn hy theo di nh.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:76:"http://www.izwebz.com/video-tutorials/css-html/fonts-for-web-font-face/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2:"14";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:42:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s: